---
import "../styles/global.css";
import { href } from "../lib/href";
import Icon from "../components/Icon.astro";

const zhHome = href("/zh/");
const jaHome = href("/ja/");
const landing = href("/");
const zhStatus = href("/zh/status/");
const jaStatus = href("/ja/status/");
const repo = "https://github.com/TUR1412/ACG";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-Hans">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>404 · ACG Radar</title>
    <meta name="description" content="页面不存在 / ページが見つかりません" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#f2f4f8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href={href("/favicon.svg")} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
      <div class="glass relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
          <div class="absolute -left-28 -top-28 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-violet-500/10 blur-3xl"></div>
          <div class="absolute -right-28 -bottom-28 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-sky-500/10 blur-3xl"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="radar grid size-12 place-items-center shadow-sm">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-white/90">ACG</span>
          </span>
          <div>
            <h1 class="m-0 text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight text-slate-950 md:text-3xl">
              404 Not Found
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-700">页面不存在 / ページが見つかりません</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="relative mt-4 text-xs text-slate-600">
          URL：
          <code id="acg-404-path" class="rounded-md bg-white/60 px-2 py-1 font-mono text-[11px] text-slate-700">
            /
          </code>
        </p>

        <div class="relative mt-6 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <a href={zhHome} class="glass clickable group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-5">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500/20 via-fuchsia-500/10 to-sky-500/15"></div>
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between">
              <div>
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950">中文</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600">返回首页</div>
              </div>
              <Icon
                name="chevron-right"
                size={18}
                class="text-slate-700 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-0.5"
              />
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href={jaHome} class="glass clickable group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-5">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-500/20 via-cyan-500/10 to-emerald-500/12"></div>
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between">
              <div>
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950">日本語</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600">ホームへ</div>
              </div>
              <Icon
                name="chevron-right"
                size={18}
                class="text-slate-700 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-0.5"
              />
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="relative mt-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-xs">
          <a
            href={zhStatus}
            class="glass clickable inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-slate-700"
            title="中文状态页"
          >
            <Icon name="info" size={14} class="text-slate-600" />
            <span>中文状态页</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href={jaStatus}
            class="glass clickable inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-slate-700"
            title="ステータス"
          >
            <Icon name="info" size={14} class="text-slate-600" />
            <span>ステータス</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href={landing}
            class="glass clickable inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-slate-700"
            title="语言选择 / 言語選択"
          >
            <Icon name="grid" size={14} class="text-slate-600" />
            <span>语言选择 / 言語選択</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href={repo}
            class="glass clickable inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 text-slate-700"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer noopener"
            title="GitHub"
          >
            <Icon name="external-link" size={14} class="text-slate-600" />
            <span>GitHub</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="relative mt-6 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          如果你是通过收藏或外部链接来到这里，可能是页面路径变更；可返回首页或查看状态页。
          <br />
          ブックマーク/外部リンクから来た場合、URLが変更された可能性があります。ホームかステータスへ戻ってください。
        </p>

        <div class="relative mt-6">
          <button
            type="button"
            id="acg-404-back"
            class="glass clickable inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-2xl px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950"
          >
            <Icon name="arrow-left" size={18} class="text-slate-700" />
            <span>返回 / 戻る</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <script is:inline>
      (() => {
        try {
          const el = document.querySelector("#acg-404-path");
          if (el) el.textContent = window.location?.pathname || "/";
          document.querySelector("#acg-404-back")?.addEventListener("click", () => {
            try {
              history.back();
            } catch {
              // ignore
            }
          });
        } catch {
          // ignore
        }
      })();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>

